➜这两条鱼的未解之谜，谁信谁傻的故事，却曾风靡整个天涯
http://www.sohu.com/a/434676263_624188	14499
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201127/281e0c4624984cb0b09cdd2f2106a7cf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在上期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕刚讲完世界十大未解之谜——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百慕大三角</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱卿立马想起了中国十大未解之谜<strong>榜首</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>双鱼玉佩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201127/5b8fddf5926d4ee186d394da6f5ba56e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕立马查了一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先弹出来的照片是这张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201127/a31dd6eb2fb546a0bb6060c9c0c80d96.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
